{"tid":1503972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［全世界入］現存白宮聯署未到期一覽","createTime":"2019-08-25T06:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T05:34:23.000Z","uid":43785,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"be4acb3e691978815ce27f5568698886ccd4ef82","tid":1503972,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"【現存白宮聯署更新】<br />\n<br />\n明白現在實在太多白宮聯署，好多人會唔記得自己簽咗邊個，我有以下建議：<br />\n<br />\n1/ 唔肯定嘅，簽多一次。在我的道德標準下，呢個可以，因為你唔係故意用同一個電郵簽幾次。<br />\n<br />\n2/ 簽咗之後，自己mark返自己簽咗邊個，這是大家的責任。<br />\n<br />\n《未夠數》<br />\n==========<br />\n中國武警冒充香港警察，白宮聯署請求美國國會盡快通過香港人權民主法案 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YW8pa8&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=bf05e280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國取消中國學生簽證<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30GcBMM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30GcBMM&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=85990a4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30GcBMM</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國派美軍拯救香港巿民<br />\n <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KsmYOQ&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=0e0d6830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國將中國共產黨定性為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MlpLM3&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=1dd0b875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國向北京施壓，停止製造白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Zkc8hX&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=6c51bb96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX</a><br />\n<br />\n拯救國泰航空，保障經濟自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZmWgPU&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=fbe42700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU</a><br />\n<br />\n要求拒絕前警務處處長曾偉雄到聯合國就任提名<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Z0cMkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Z0cMkw&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=78b58ce8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Z0cMkw</a><br />\n🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n《以下夠數，但到期前越多人越好》<br />\n==========<br />\n請求美國派出醫療船支援香港 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2H221Iu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H221Iu&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=2c543426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2H221Iu</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國國會確認香港警察為恐怖組織 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KzVVQB&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=582416a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB</a><br />\n<br />\n請美國國會提名【爭取民主自由的香港人】競逐諾貝爾和平獎，藉以保護義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZbGdQH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZbGdQH&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=d5334263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZbGdQH</a><br />\n<br />\n簽名＞等電郵＞確認簽名＞傳開去"},{"pid":"021d8ba3b2a92f26dfddc712b154e234e3dfdecb","tid":1503972,"uid":174432,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sO1pgvB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsO1pgvB.png&h=8e442698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGood afternoon Sir!"},{"pid":"bac84d9a32de5b2e3d4a5f3aa5f48f1142514aa2","tid":1503972,"uid":214777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:53:18.000Z","msg":"你點影的"},{"pid":"d42e841304f5e0623f5ca7d06cea38e3c60e70c7","tid":1503972,"u